    "• Sentences shorter than 10 and longer than 40 words were removed, as upon initial data exploration such content often turned out to be boilerplate material.",
    "The size of the preprocessed corpus of documents was 251,376 tokens, its vocabulary containing 15,614 unique words.",
    "The mean length of a document was 920.8 words (σ =635.7).",
    "The mean number of sentences in a document was 45.5 (σ =31.6).",
    "The target variable, pledged amount, was log-transformed to diminish the effect of extreme values."
